H0.text: Said to be the birthplace of the rules of Association Football, Parker’s Piece is in which English city. Oxford

H1.text: Said to be the birthplace of the rules of Association Football, Parker’s Piece is in which English city. Manchester

H2.text: Said to be the birthplace of the rules of Association Football, Parker’s Piece is in which English city. Birmingham

H3.text: Said to be the birthplace of the rules of Association Football, Parker’s Piece is in which English city. Cambridge

A4.text: Parker's Piece is located near the centre of Cambridge, England.

A5.text: The Cambridge University Football Club Laws were first used on Parker's Piece and adopted by the Football Association in 1863.
